==Russian==
===Noun===
'''икра́''' (ikrá) {{f}}

#''(only singular)'' [[roe]], [[spawn]] (''of fish''), also small eggs of [[frog|frogs]] or other [[Amphibia]]
#: [[метать|мета́ть]] икру́ — ''to [[spawn]]''
#''(only singular)'' [[caviar]], (1) as food
#: [[зернистый|зерни́стая]] икра́ — ''[[soft]] caviar''
#: [[кетовый|кето́вая]] икра́ — ''[[red]] caviar''
#: [[устричная|у́стричная]] икра́ — ''[[spat]]''
#''(only singular)'' {{figurative}} [[paste]] (meal of mushrooms or vegetables cut into small particles)
#: [[баклажанный|баклажа́нная]] икра́ — ''[[aubergine]] paste''
#: [[кабачковый|кабачко́вая]] икра́ — ''[[marrow]] paste''
#: [[грибной|грибна́я]] икра́ — ''[[mushroom]] paste''
#''(usually plural)'' [[calf]] of the leg, (''musculus gastrocnemius'') [[gastrocnemius]] [[muscle]]
#: [[играть|игра́ть]] и́крами — ''(literally) to play with the calves'' (repeatedly quickly tensing and relaxing the calves of the legs)
#{{obsolete}} [[drifting]] [[ice-floe]] ''(especially on a river)''

